        "text": "Thanks. Will it be moved to the 'r-release' version eventually, since e.g., the NEWS R 4.5.2 is also there? And where can I read about the differences between, and uses of, r-release, r-devel, and r-patched? (I thought that r-devel would become r-release and I was not aware of there being a 'patched' version so am now wondering where that fits in).",
